translations: n.常乘飞机旅行的富人（同 jet-setter）

sentences.sentence: Last fall, you launched a number of subsections such as Gilt Man, and Jetsetter for travel deals.
sentences.translation: 去年秋天，你们推出了数款旅行套装，如Gilt Man, and Jetsetter。

sentences.sentence: On Jetsetter, one of the surprising things has been how quickly the hotels and resorts have recognized the marketing opportunity.
sentences.translation: 至于Jetsetter，宾馆和度假村那么迅速地意识到营销机会，令人惊讶。
